title: DATED
name: Date of Agency Authorization
definition: Identifies the date appearing on the agency authorization, which was previously submitted to the provider.
validEntries: U.S. Standard  Metric Format  T wo Digit Month  ( 01-12)  T wo Digit Century  ( 00-99)  T wo Digit Day  ( 01-31)  T wo Digit Year  ( 00-99)  T wo Digit Century  ( 00-99)  T wo Digit Month  ( 01-12)  T wo Digit Year  ( 00-99)  T wo Digit Day  ( 01-31)
usageNotes: Required when the AGAUTH field is "E" or "B", otherwise optional.
